subject: Basketball
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: Tyler Hansbrough had 29 points and 9 rebounds, and No. 2 North Carolina pulled away in the second half for a 103-81 victory against Sacred Heart in the opening round of the N.I.T. Season Tip-Off.
